In 2021, Piney Point, MD had a population of 939 people with a median age of 42.5 and a median household income of $123,563. Between 2020 and 2021 the population of Piney Point, MD declined from 1,036 to 939, a −9.36% decrease.<ref>{{cite web | url=https://datausa.io/profile/geo/piney-point-md | title=Piney Point, MD &#124; Data USA }}</ref>

